    {
      question: "Are DigiStorms and Resend competitors?",
      answer: "Not exactly — they solve different problems. Resend is an email sending API for developers who want to build their own email infrastructure with React Email templates. DigiStorms is a done-for-you AI onboarding agent: we analyze your product, map your activation milestones, then write and run the sequence for you. You could even use them together — DigiStorms to design and drive the onboarding strategy, Resend to send the mail.",
